# ğŸ¥ Skin Disease Chatbot

This is a **multimodal chatbot** that predicts **skin diseases** using **text, images, and audio inputs**.  
It utilizes **Deep Learning (PyTorch)** for image classification and **Google Gemini AI** for text/audio-based diagnosis.

